    <relatedmaterial encodinganalog="1.8B18">
      <p>For other records relating to the establishment and activities of the Reading and Study Centre, see series F-107-1-2-4 and F-107-3-2-12 in the Student Services fonds (F-107). Correspondence relating to the Centre can also be found in series F-193-17-1, Office of the President fonds &gt; Reading and Study Centre (1967-1981); and F-207-4-3, Office of the Vice-President, University Services &gt; Reading and Study Centre (1971-1976).</p>
    </relatedmaterial>
    <accessrestrict encodinganalog="1.8B16a">
      <p>The files are open with no restrictions. Access to the audio recordings is restricted due to the age and fragility of the storage medium (cassette tapes). Access is provided via digitized copy.</p>
    </accessrestrict>
